    • Constructor Detail

      • Client

        public Client(java.lang.String ip,
              java.lang.String arg)
        Constructor for client class. If argument 0 is singleplayer, starts TerminalInputHandler in SINGLEPLAYER state. Elseif argument is AI starts in AI state. Checks other args for difficulty and whether print statements should be silenced Else (normal) starts it normally Then executes connect method
        Parameters:
        ip - ip address to connect to in string format
        arg - Arguments for construction in string format
